{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_51_01",
  "title": "fran 1話 クソガキに鉄槌を",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "franさ～ん。聞きましたわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fran-san~. I heard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6999999166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もうすぐ、franさんのお誕生日……あら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your birthday is coming up soon… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666665833,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.333416699999,
          "startTime": 9.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "この先生も違う……こっちの先生もイメージとは……\nはぁ……この調子で誕生日までに間に合うのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This artist isn’t right either… And this one isn’t what I imagined…\nSigh… I wonder if I can make it in time for my birthday like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333332499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "何か悩み事ですの？　って……まぁ！\n漫画の本がこんなに沢山。一体どうしたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s bothering you? …Oh my!\nYou have so many manga! What’s going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333332499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あー、気にしないで。今度の『ミラクル☆\nアイドルバースデー！』で使う資料だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Ahー don’t worry about it. It’s just reference material\nfor the upcoming “Miracle☆ Idol Birthday!”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4666665833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それって、アイドルがやってみたいことを叶えてくれる\n雑誌のお誕生日企画ですわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the birthday project in the magazine\nwhere they grant an idol’s wish‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3333368104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "franさんにもお話が来たんですのね！\nどんなお願いをするんですの？　この漫画と関係が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You got an offer for it too‚ fran-san!\nWhat kind of wish are you going to make? Does it have to do with this manga?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう、忙しいんだから絡まないでよ……\n分かったから。説明してあげるから静かにして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I’m busy‚ so leave me alone.\nFine‚ fine. I’ll explain‚ so be quiet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6000016969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、『漫画の原作に挑戦したい』……\nそれがfranさんのやってみたいことですのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ “trying your hand at writing a manga”…\nThat’s what you want to do‚ fran-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8333329957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、それで絵を描いてくれる人を探してたって訳\nせっかくなら、好きな先生に頼みたいでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ so I’ve been looking for someone to draw for me.\nIf I’m going to do this‚ I want to ask an artist I like‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2333329957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね。自分の考えたお話を、大好きな先生が\n漫画にしてくれる。夢のようなお願いですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true. it’d be a dream come true to have a story\nyou wrote drawn by an artist you love!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9333329957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "有名な漫画雑誌を出してる出版社だし、もともと私も\n漫画が好きだから。ちょうどいいなって思ったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a publishing house that puts out a famous manga magazine‚ and I’ve always\nloved manga. I thought it would be a perfect fit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1333340129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、漫画がお好きだったなんて、初めて知りましたわ\nここにある漫画も、たぶん私物ですわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I had no idea you liked manga.\nI’m guessing all this manga is yours?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9000006796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "い、今まで公表しにくかったのよ。漫画が好きとか\nオタクっぽいっていうか……イメージと違うかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ it was hard to say it out loud. Liking manga\nsounds kind of otaku-ish… I thought it didn’t fit my image.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2666673463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないと思いますけど……\nでも、それならなぜ今になって……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think so…\nBut then why now…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1333340129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "最近タレントさんの中にも、普通に公表してる人がいる\nでしょ？　しかもそれが、人気に繋がっていたりするし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These days there are even celebrities who openly talk about liking manga‚ right?\nAnd sometimes it even leads to more popularity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5000006796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "なら私も、公表してもいいんじゃないかって思って\nそれに、特に最近は、ほら……kanaが話題だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I thought‚ maybe it’s okay for me to talk about it too.\nBesides‚ especially lately‚ you know… kana’s been getting a lot of attention…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9333340129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、漫画原作の映画に出たのを機に\n漫画好きを公表していたような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ I think she said\nshe likes manga after being in that movie…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4000006796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "よく、漫画の感想をSNSに投稿してますし\n漫画関係のイベントにも呼ばれていましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She often posts her thoughts on manga on social media‚\nand she’s been invited to manga-related events.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.0000016969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　それが許せないのもあって決断したのよ\n前から漫画が好きだった？　漫画はよく読む方？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! That’s what made me decide to do this.\n“I’ve always loved manga”‚ “I read a lot of manga”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "漫画なんてろくに読んでなかったくせして嘘ばっかり\nあんな媚び売ってるだけのにわかは、爆発するべきよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s been lying through her teeth‚ pretending she’s read a bunch when she hasn’t.\nThat fake fan who's just sucking up for attention should just blow up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.1666683635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "この機会に、私が話題も仕事も根こそぎ奪って\nなんちゃって漫画好きのクソガキに鉄槌を下してやるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to use this opportunity to snatch away all her attention and work‚\nand bring the hammer of justice down on that fake manga-loving brat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "漫画への愛情は伝わってきましたが、それ以上に\n私怨が凄いですわね……。が、頑張ってくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your love for manga is clear‚ but\nyour grudge is even stronger… W-well‚ good luck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.4333350302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "伝わった？　じゃあ説明代、千円ね\nわざわざ手を止めて、相手してあげたんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You got it? Then that’ll be 1‚000 yen for the explanation.\nI stopped what I was doing to explain it to you‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.1000016969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことでお金を要求しないでくださいまし！？\nあと、お金が掛かるなら事前に説明してくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t ask for money for something like that!?\nAnd if it’s going to cost money‚ you should tell me beforehand!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.1433233065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.484897435,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1481.7710119000083,
          "startTime": 213.9666684469
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 213.5515702052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま戻りましたわ～\n……って、franさん、まだいらっしゃいましたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m back~.\n…Oh‚ fran-san‚ you’re still here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.3000088177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないでしょ、全然描いてくれる先生が決まらない\nんだから。いい先生がいても、予定が合わないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can’t be helped‚ I haven’t found an artist yet.\nEven if I find a good artist‚ their schedule doesn’t work out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.1666754844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
