      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "編集部があげてくれる候補は、イメージと違ったりして\n悩ましいったらないわ。……あ、それよりすず、千円",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The candidates the editorial department gives me don’t match my image‚\nit’s so frustrating. …Oh‚ by the way‚ Suzu‚ 1‚000 yen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.1666754844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "さらっと請求しないでくださいまし……\nでも、それならいい案がありますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don’t just casually ask me for money…\nBut if you’re looking for ideas‚ I have a good one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.6333360476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "絵は、この私に任せるというのはどうでしょう\nなんと私は、絵のコンクールで金賞を取った実力者――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about leaving the drawing to me?\nI am‚ after all‚ a talented artist who won a gold prize in an art competition――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.5666704815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "あー、すず、やっぱり千円は今度でいいわ\nもう帰っていいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah~ Suzu‚ you can give me the 1‚000 yen later.\nYou can go home now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.1666632774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_51_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "聞かなかったことにしないでくださいまし！\n仕方ないですわね、では私の絵をお見せしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t just ignore me!\nFine‚ I’ll show you my art.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.8999783002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
