      "text": "そ、それは一理ありますが、練習すれば描けますわ！\nこれだけの画力があれば、漫画の絵だって余裕です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that’s true‚ but I can learn if I practice!\nWith this much artistic talent‚ manga art should be a piece of cake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.099970162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
